@Repository public interface StaffRepository extends tk.mybatis.mapper.common.Mapper<Staff>
This interface defines a repository for Staff entities. It extends the Mapper interface from MyBatis to provide basic CRUD operations. Additional custom methods are defined using MyBatis annotations.

  • Method Details

    • findById

      @Select("select * from staff where userID = #{userID} limit 1") Staff findById(@Param("userID") String userID)
      Retrieves a Staff entity from the database based on the userID.
      Parameters:
      userID - The userID of the staff member.
      Returns:
      The Staff entity matching the userID, or null if not found.

    • findByIDAndPasswd

      @Select("select * from staff where userID = #{userID} and userPassword = #{userPassword} limit 1") Staff findByIDAndPasswd(@Param("userID") String userID, @Param("userPassword") String userPassword)
      Retrieves a Staff entity from the database based on the userID and password.
      Parameters:
      userID - The userID of the staff member.
      userPassword - The password of the staff member.
      Returns:
      The Staff entity matching the userID and password, or null if not found.

    • updatePassword

      @Update("UPDATE staff SET userPassword = #{userPassword} WHERE userID = #{userID}") void updatePassword(@Param("userID") String userID, @Param("userPassword") String userPassword)
      Updates the password of a staff member in the database.
      Parameters:
      userID - The userID of the staff member.
      userPassword - The new password to be set.
